  "abstract": "The Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System is proposing to amend Subpart A of Regulation H, regarding the general provisions for membership in the Federal Reserve System, and Subpart E of Regulation H, regarding Interpretations, in order to reduce regulatory burden and simplify and update requirements. The proposal would also eliminate several obsolete interpretations. The Board is also reissuing existing Subparts B and C. Existing Subparts B and C would not be significantly amended bu",
